## Update Custom Field Option

```http
PATCH https://api.teamtailor.com/v1/custom-field-options/1 HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Token token=abc123abc123
X-Api-Version: <%= config[:api_version] %>

{
  "data": {
    "id": 1,
    "type": "custom-field-options",
    "attributes": {
      "value": "Updated value",
    }
  }
}
```

```shell
curl -X "PATCH" "https://api.teamtailor.com/v1/custom-field-options/1" \
     -H "Authorization: Token token=abc123abc123" \
     -H "X-Api-Version: <%= config[:api_version] %>"
     -H "Content-Type: application/vnd.api+json" \
     -d '{
   "data": {
     "id": 1,
     "type": "custom-field-options",
     "attributes": {
       "value": "Updated value"
     }
   }
}'
```

